	<string id="ui_mcm_auto_looter_disassemble_misc_description">
		<text>Given that some of the misc items' parts are near to worthless and tasks for the whole item might give you some better reward (e. g. porn magazines), you can define below what kind of misc items should and should not be disassembled.</text>
